reviewText: Excellent stories, excellent telling... very happy I bought the three together.

I had hoped that there, would of been @ least 2 more love scenes between lisbeth, & her co-star, that, ran the paper, I think that, the last 2 love scenes, the first love scene when she first came back, from being gone so long, in the second movie, & again in the last movie. I was bumbed out that, lisbeth & her costar didn't get two more love scenes, that, was a good pairing.
Love it, cheap and nothing different from the rest

I had the fist DVD, however ordered the trilogy just to see what happens to the Character. Re-viewed the first part, started the 2nd DVD and couldn't stop till I watched the 3rd DVD. So much better than the American version with Daniel Craig. Some scenes hard to watch but supported the growth of the Character. Highly recommend if you like a thriller or Books of this type.
the best. so much fun to watch, fine camera work and superb acting. Disks were perfect, great price.
Bought for wife. She loved it and I loved the price. Same DVD/Bluray as other combos for half the price.
